      <title>普华永道面临中国客户和员工流失问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pwc-is-struggling-in-china-with-an-exodus-of-clients-and-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普华永道会计师事务所 (PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP) 在中国的监管问题已导致其客户大批流失，部分会计师也因此跳槽至竞争对手，令该公司在世界第二大经济体的前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pwc-is-struggling-in-china-with-an-exodus-of-clients-and-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
