      <title>特朗普胜选交易增多，全球市场警惕拜登退欧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿关于总统乔·拜登是否放弃竞选连任的激烈辩论正在蔓延到华尔街，交易员们正在将资金转移到美元、美国国债和其他可能受唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫影响的资产上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/wall-street-on-alert-for-biden-exit-as-trump-win-trades-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 17:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡与债券持有人达成重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/sri-lanka-bondholders-agree-on-core-terms-of-debt-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡与债权人达成协议，重组价值 126 亿美元的债券，这使得这个南亚国家在债务违约两年后更接近完成债务改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/sri-lanka-bondholders-agree-on-core-terms-of-debt-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
